BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed article: "Council Decides Contribution To </F>
EBRD Nuclear Safety Account"; as released by EUROPE] 
  [Text] The Council of the European Union has adopted the 
decision on conclusion of the agreement (in the form of an 
exchange of letters) negotiated by the European Commission 
concerning the Community contribution of ECU20 million to the 
EBRD's (European Bank for Reconstruction and Development) 
nuclear safety account. The money is to be used to improve the 
safety of nuclear power stations in Central and East European 
countries and the republics of the ex-USSR. 

